<br>
Ive seen the new Barnacle Covered Axe sell for &lt; 1k which IMHO is an excellent aggro weapon for the cost.<br>
<br>
Also look into the Praetors Blade of Debility (sp) quest, its really rather easy and its a nice little aggro proc.<br>
